Class ResponseWrapper<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.extensia.xcp.services.restapi.model.ResponseWrapper<T>

    T - Type parameter for data class encapsulated by the wrapper
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ResponseListWrapper

    public class ResponseWrapper<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    Generic class used to provide the standard response fields and behaviors common to REST response messages.
